<td align="center"><b>
<i>Nomada citrina</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">Cresson, 1878</font></b><br>
<small><i>Nomada &#40;Heminomada&#41; citrina </i>Cresson, 1878; <i>Nomada &#40;Heminomada&#41; citrina flavomarginata </i>Swenk, 1913; <i>Nomada citrina var rufula </i>Cockerell, 1903; <i>Nomada &#40;Heminomada&#41; citrina rufula </i>Cockerell, 1903; <i>Nomada citrina flavomarginata </i>Swenk, 1913, valid subspecies; <i>Nomada citrina rufula </i>Cockerell, 1903, valid subspecies</small><p>
